<a href="/logOut" style="color:green; float: right">LOG-OUT</a>

<h3> Nice to have you on board {{ name }}, would you like to provide us with some more information about yourself? </h3>

<form method="POST" id="profile_form">

         <input
            name="age"
            type="number"
            min="18" 
            max="99"
            class="user-data"
            id="age"
            placeholder="Your age"
        />

        <input
            name="city"
            type="text"
            pattern="[\p{Letter}\-'ßñÄÖÜäüöæÆÅåØø]+"
            class="user-data"
            id="city"
            placeholder="Your city"
        />

        <input
            name="homepage"
            type="url"
            class="user-data"
            id="homepage"
            placeholder="Your Homepage"
        />
        

        <input type="submit" value="Edit Info" />

        <p style="color:red" > {{ error }} </p>

    </form>

    <h4> If you want to keep that to yourself, no problem, go directly to <a href="/main">SIGN</a> our petition.</h4>